	<dl>
	<dt>I can't be bothered to choose one load...</dt>
	<dd><p>I can't be bothered to choose one load of lies over another...<br />Although I would vote for the party that taxed you more the poorer you were....and paid zero dole money.</p> <p>Why? well it would encourage them to work harder and make them pay for their cost to society, let's face it the majority of chavs running riot are from poor backgrounds and cause more damage,crime, violence,cost more in policing than people from families that are hard working and discipline their kids at home.</p> <p></p>
	<small>
	written 12th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/716">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=716">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

